    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >洪水迫在眉睫，方舟恭候大驾。</h2><br>在命运的安排下，我们的英雄们发现了一艘避难的方舟。然而，当他们抵达方舟大门时，却被无情地拒之门外，因为自私的花栗鼠国王已将上层甲板的所有位置都占满了！对这些无座可坐的动物们来说，他们只有一个选择：推翻暴君花栗鼠。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控玩家对战节奏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/f032f3fdf6b3f53a2d09125c4c7d7d82.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>畅玩异步多人游戏，尽享战斗乐趣！在竞技场模式中，轻松与其他玩家队伍对战，赢取十次胜利。你能击败所有对手，成为最后的幸存者吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验完整剧情战役</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/d03317f711b02d071c7f28bef8834b15.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>洪水迫在眉睫，只有方舟可救苍生。然而... 邪恶的花栗鼠国王强占了所有坐席！在充满手绘动画和艺术设计的美妙世界中，完成单人战役，磨练技能，踏上自我救赎的征途。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从贵族猫到健身鼠</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.poster.avif?t=1762957880\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.webm?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/8bfc764c0ba33e888c766bd98a1e0c3e.mp4?t=1762957880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索奇幻动物王国，收集并塑造各种萌趣可爱的动物。你将遇到野蛮熊、刺客猫、武士柴犬，还有... 宅男仓鼠？了解他们的强项、弱点和配合效果，打造你的梦幻团队。",
